<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>의사 대시보드 - MediCare+</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script src="/js/feather.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
  
  {{> components/sidebar}}

  <div class="main-content">
    {{> components/header}}
    
    <main class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="space-y-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">의사 대시보드</h1>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
                <i data-feather="users" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">오늘 진료 환자 수</div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">{{todayPatientCount}}명</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-green-600">
                <i data-feather="check-circle" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">진료 완료</div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">{{completedCount}}명</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-orange-600">
                <i data-feather="clock" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">현재 대기 중</div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">{{waitingCount}}명</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 flex items-center gap-2">
              <i data-feather="calendar" class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600"></i>
              오늘의 진료 일정 미리 보기
            </h2>
            <a href="/treatments" class="text-sm text-indigo-600 font-medium flex items-center gap-1 hover:text-indigo-800">
              진료 목록 전체보기 <i data-feather="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            {{#schedulePreview}}
            <a href="{{#isCompleted}}/treatments/completed{{/isCompleted}}{{^isCompleted}}/treatments/{{id}}{{/isCompleted}}" 
               class="block p-4 rounded-xl border transition-all cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md 
                      {{#isInProgress}}bg-indigo-50 border-indigo-200 ring-2 ring-indigo-100{{/isInProgress}}
                      {{#isCompleted}}bg-slate-50 border-slate-200 opacity-60{{/isCompleted}}
                      {{^isInProgress}}{{^isCompleted}}bg-white border-slate-200{{/isCompleted}}{{/isInProgress}}">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-500">{{time}}</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-lg 
                             {{#isInProgress}}bg-indigo-600 text-white{{/isInProgress}}
                             {{#isCompleted}}bg-slate-200 text-slate-600{{/isCompleted}}
                             {{#isReceived}}bg-orange-100 text-orange-600{{/isReceived}}
                             {{#isReserved}}bg-slate-100 text-slate-400{{/isReserved}}">
                  {{statusText}}
                </span>
              </div>
              <div class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-1">{{name}}</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 truncate">{{symptoms}}</div>
            </a>
            {{/schedulePreview}}

            {{^schedulePreview}}
            <div class="col-span-full p-12 text-center text-slate-500 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-slate-300">
              오늘 예정된 진료 일정이 없습니다.
            </div>
            {{/schedulePreview}}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    {{> components/footer}}
  </div>

  <script>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
      feather.replace();
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>